      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DEADLY POWER (3) has a strong record this track and trip with three wins and four placings from eight starts. Recorded a half a length win (19.50) in a Grade 5 last time at Hobart. Looks well placed and should feature. DUSTY RICO (7) did a good job to finish third last time out over 340m at Hobart (19.69) in a Grade 5, the second top-three finish on the trot. Can hit the frame this time. BIG TEXAN (6) had been racing well with a Other win three back then placed next time before missing the frame latest at Hobart. Well placed here and can atone this time. FISHY BUSINESS (2) is always hard to beat when she races at this trip.",
